Steps :

1. Go to Github and open the option Developer Settings.
2. Create an OAuth application with respective details:
    * ApplicationName : Name your application with the desired name
    * Homepage URL    : http://localhost:8080/
    * Authorization   : http://localhost:8080/login/oauth2/code/github
    
 3. Create a client Secret Key and configure application.yml or application.properties in spring boot application
 
 spring:
  security:
    oauth2:
      client:
        registration:
           github:
              client-id: a3244d29cb865c119f4a
              client-secret: 1bf5ec360320bcfa3163c7394dd4a90efbbab4ca 
